    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> beluga lentils </strong>to the dish with the <strong>dried oregano</strong> and give everything a good mix</p><p>Wash your <strong>lamb's lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
