    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add in your<strong> vegetable stock mix<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>with your<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>tomato paste</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and 400m<span class=\"text-purple\">l [520ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[680ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Stir through your<strong> Marmite</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat – this is your <strong>pie filling</strong></p>",
