    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into discs</p><p>Carefully arrange the<strong> potato discs</strong> over the top of the pie filling</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 40 min or until everything's bubbling and the potatoes are cooked through – this is your <strong>all-in-one hearty mushroom & lentil pie</strong></p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p>",
